item.title: Ausiello TV
item.description: Michael Ausiello: You’re back this season Jorja Fox: Maybe. Maybe I am, maybe I’m not. Ausiello: I’ve already seen the first episode, and you were there. Fox: Yeah, yeah. I’m definitely there for that. Ausiello: And a couple more there. Fox: Yeah, I’m visiting for a little bit. I’ll be in and out, so that’s kind of fun. I knew that might happen, I didn’t know it was gonna happen so soon.
